---
title: Caribbean Pork Rissoles & Coconut Chilli Mayo with Spiced Wedges & Pineapple Salsa
description: Add a medley of mild spice to your rissoles by giving them a little island flair! Straight from the Caribbean, this jerk seasoning
brings unmistakeable flavour and fun to the humble rissole. Paired with a fresh pineapple salsa and coconut sweet chilli mayo,
this is a colourful take on a classic dinner.
